                <UserObject label="&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 36px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;🚫 Shared-Nothing&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;Each server owns its data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;Architecture:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;Server 1 → Room 1-1000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;Server 2 → Room 1001-2000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;Server 3 → Room 2001-3000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;✅ Advantages:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;• No distributed locks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;• No contention&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;• No sync overhead&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;❌ Disadvantages:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;• Partitioning complexity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;• Data redistribution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;📊 Usage:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;• Ludo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;• WhatsApp&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;• Large-scale chat&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" mermaidId="n:K" mermaidBaseStyle="html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=2;fillColor=#0f3460;strokeColor=#e94560;fontColor=#ffffff;fontFamily=Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Arial,sans-serif;fontSize=16;" mermaidBaseValue="🚫 Shared-Nothing&#xa;&#xa;Each server owns its data&#xa;&#xa;Architecture:&#xa;Server 1 → Room 1-1000&#xa;Server 2 → Room 1001-2000&#xa;Server 3 → Room 2001-3000&#xa;&#xa;✅ Advantages:&#xa;• No distributed locks&#xa;• No contention&#xa;• No sync overhead&#xa;&#xa;❌ Disadvantages:&#xa;• Partitioning complexity&#xa;• Data redistribution&#xa;&#xa;📊 Usage:&#xa;• Ludo&#xa;• WhatsApp&#xa;• Large-scale chat" id="23">
